Global Potassium Citrate Granules Market Insights
Potassium Citrate Granules Market size was valued at USD 0.85 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.15 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 4.3% from 2024 to 2030.

Potassium Citrate Granules Market Overview
The Potassium Citrate Granules Market has been experiencing significant growth in recent years. The market's value is expected to reach approximately USD 1.2 billion by 2026, expanding at a CAGR of 6.5% during the forecast period. This growth is driven by increasing demand from the pharmaceutical, food & beverage, and dietary supplement industries. Potassium Citrate Granules are widely utilized for their benefits in managing kidney stones, improving cardiovascular health, and enhancing electrolyte balance. Moreover, the expanding awareness about health and wellness has contributed to the rising consumption of potassium-based products in various applications.

